{"tid":946980,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"[只係調整同不明朗, 沒事]【外圍充滿挑戰】陳茂波：港前景持續不明朗","createTime":"2018-12-19T02:29:23.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-19T06:17:21.000Z","uid":57424,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"0bb02f0c6588a32f0b415ed72fa7cf0a73937a8b","tid":946980,"uid":57424,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-19T02:29:23.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.now.com/home/finance/player?newsId=331204\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Ffinance%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D331204&d=MgGw1fxvt6eEJPHkMJ7ZSttKgwQIhJBw7VlnLihElrQ%3D&h=5a5ef43b\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Ffinance%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D331204&h=28d928d0\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.now.com/home/finance/player?newsId=331204</a><br />\n【Now新聞台】財政司司長陳茂波表示，樓巿過去數月有秩序地調整，但現時樓價仍大幅超出巿民的負擔能力。他又指，明年外圍環境充滿挑戰，本港前景持續不明朗。<br />\n<br />\n近期樓市轉趨淡靜，長陳茂波在立法會匯報本港經濟狀況時表示，受中美貿易戰及加息等不利因素影響，本港樓市8月起調整，轉趨淡靜，10月整體住宅售價較7月高位下跌約4%，但過去數月是有秩序的調整。<br />\n<br />\n陳茂波又指，中美貿易磨擦升溫等因素，亦令本港營商氣氛變得審慎，今年全年經濟增長預測為3.2%，展望明年外圍環充滿挑戰，前景持續不明朗。<br />\n<br />\n另外，陳茂波表示，政府會繼續審慎的金融監管，維持穩健公共財政，令香港有足夠能力應對外來衝擊。<br />\n又贏<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"805864fd854015704a6010dea4d837850530ee55","tid":946980,"uid":195998,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-19T02:46:55.000Z","msg":"廢淡"},{"pid":"f8407ec6fa7640a685737fd6d6751811fcedb75c","tid":946980,"uid":92734,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-19T05:59:51.000Z","msg":"回歸後有邊年明朗架挑"},{"pid":"c40c591f10f886a17450c20712f394516d4bf32a","tid":946980,"uid":57424,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"f8407ec6fa7640a685737fd6d6751811fcedb75c","tid":946980,"uid":92734,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-19T05:59:51.000Z","msg":"回歸後有邊年明朗架挑"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-19T06:17:21.000Z","msg":"2008年澳運<br />\n全港大中華膠<br />\n國家欣欣向榮<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}